const getDummies = (titleType) => {
  let dummyData;

      'java',

      'mysql',

      'centos',
      'windows',
      'mac',
      'c',
      'c#',
      'c++',

      'a',

    ];
  }
  if (TITLE_TYPE_QUESTION === titleType) {
    dummyData = [
      '1. When you have faults, do not fear to abandon them. – Confucius',
      '2. They must often change who would be constant in happiness or wisdom. – Confucius',

      '5. You will face many defeats in life, but never let yourself be defeated. – Maya Angelou',

      '17. Life is from the inside out. When you shift on the inside, life shifts on the outside. – Kamal Ravikant',
      '18. Life can only be understood backwards; but it must be lived forwards. – Søren Kierkegaard',
      '19. Despite the forecast, live like it’s spring. – Lilly Pulitzer',
      '20. The two most important days in your life are the day you are born and the day you find out why. – Mark Twain',
    ];
  }
  if (TITLE_TYPE_ANSWERS === titleType) {
    dummyData = [
      'I have to get this done today.',
      'I have to make new plans for the New year.',
      'I have to admit that Korean students are really brilliant and hard-working.',
      'I don’t have to hand this in today.',
      'I don’t have to protect her.',
      'I don’t have to go to school tomorrow.',
      'I’m gonna have to tell her how I feel.',
      'I’m gonna have to wear thick clothes.',
      'I’m gonna have to study for my exam this weekend.',

      'All you have to do is trust me.',

  }
  const result = [];
  for (const tag of dummyData) {
    if (Math.random() < 0.5) result.push(tag);
    return result;
  }
  console.log(dummyData);

};
